  Default:              False

Flag pcache
  Description:          Enable the persistent caching of the compiled CUDA modules (experimental)
  Default:              False

Flag test-suite
  Description:          Export extra test modules
  Default:              False

Flag bounds-checks
  Description:          Enable bounds checking
  Default:              True

Flag unsafe-checks
